    <div><p><a title="Companies > Capcom [2,611 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> has announced “brother <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,782 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a>” collection <em><a title="Games > Mega Man Star Force: Legacy Collection" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mega-man-star-force-legacy-collection">Mega Man Star Force: Legacy Collection</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,349 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,890 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,336 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,181 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,653 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,219 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> (Steam). It will launch in 2026. <span id="more-991615"></span></p><p>The collection includes the following titles:</p><ul><li><em>Mega Man Star Force Leo</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force Dragon</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force Pegasus</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force 2 Zerker x Ninja</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force 2 Zerker x Saurian</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force 3 Black Ace</em></li><li><em>Mega Man Star Force 3 Red Joker</em></li><li>Online – From battling to trading cards, the powered up online functions will let you experience the Mega Man series at its finest!</li></ul><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
